high_descs: Walk past the fridge across the room and turn right to face the black table at the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the black table.
Turn around and walk forward and turn to the left to face the table to the right of the stove.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn right and walk forward to face the black table.
Place the knife on the black table.
Turn to the left to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from on the table.
Take a step to the left and face the back right burner.
Place the slice of lettuce in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan with the lettuce slice in it.
Turn to the right and walk to face the far end of the table.
Place the pan with the lettuce slice in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: To cut a slice of lettuce plus insert it into a pan as well as move the pan from the stove to the table.

high_descs: Walk to the other end of the room in the direction of the long white table, hang a right to the small brown table.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the back of the brown table.
Turn and walk to the left end of the long white table where there is a cabbage.
Slice the cabbage on the long white table.
Turn to your right while carrying the knife.
Walk to the small brown table and place the knife at the back of the table.
Turn around and walk to the sliced cabbage at the end of the long white table.
Pick up an end slice of the cabbage.
Move to stand in front of the stove to the left of the long white table.
Place the cabbage slice in the pan on the front right burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the cabbage slice in it using the handle of the pan.
Turn to your right and walk to the other end of the long white table.
Place the pan with the cabbage in it at the right end of the table nearest the small brown table.
anns.task_desc: Slice cabbage, put in a pan, place the pan at the other end of the table

high_descs: Head to the small black table
Grab the large knife off of the table
Turn around and go to the left side of the white table
Cut the cabbage on the table into slices
Turn right and stop at the black table
Put the knife on the black table
Turn around and go to the white table
Grab a slice of cabbage
Turn left and go to the oven
Put the cabbage in the pan in the bottom right stove
Grab the pan in the bottom right stove
Turn right and head to the right side of the white table
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan with a slice of cabbage in it on the white table
